Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.47,0:02:09.05,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}満開の愛を載せて　笑顔  届きますように
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.06,0:02:19.66,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}新しい世界の始まり　My Dear　Dear
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.77,0:02:25.67,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,イージーだった私に　論外全部サヨナラ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.69,0:02:29.33,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}後悔なんで　もうしないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.65,0:02:37.41,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,どんな困難なことも　ハッピーに変換したら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.42,0:02:43.24,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}Shine  朝日も手招きしているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.25,0:02:46.19,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,不安にこっそり震えてても強がって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.25,0:02:49.22,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,胸　ギュッと振り絞ったら加速して
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.26,0:02:55.21,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,勇気感じる　だって君がすぐ傍に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.25,0:03:01.22,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}一緒にどこまでも　進もう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.23,0:03:08.39,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}乗っちゃった追い風に　精一杯　届けたいからね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.40,0:03:13.18,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}君へと繋ぐココロ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.22,0:03:21.05,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}最新のコラムに　めいいっばい　気持ち込めたから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.06,0:03:29.87,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)}ときめいて　どこでも行けるよ　My Dear　My Dear
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.47,0:02:09.05,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}載上盛放的愛  希望笑容能夠送達
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.06,0:02:19.66,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}新世界的開始  My Dear  Dear
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.77,0:02:25.67,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,曾經安逸的我  告別所有的不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.69,0:02:29.33,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}已經不會再後悔了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.65,0:02:37.41,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是怎樣的困難  也要設法變成快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.42,0:02:43.24,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}Shine  朝陽也在招手喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.25,0:02:46.19,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,不安時偷偷地顫抖也要逞強
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.25,0:02:49.22,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,揪緊了心一口氣全力加速
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.26,0:02:55.21,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,感受到了勇氣  因為你就在我身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.25,0:03:01.22,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}一起走遍天涯海角吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.23,0:03:08.39,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}乘上了愛之風  竭盡全力去傳遞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.40,0:03:13.18,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}和你相連的心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.22,0:03:21.05,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}在最新的新聞欄裡  將所有的心情都傾注進去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.06,0:03:29.87,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)}心跳不已  無論何處都能前往  My Dear  My Dear
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.94,0:00:17.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的天氣也很好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.02,0:00:23.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好  努力做早飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.75,0:00:27.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.04,0:00:30.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今早是開拓味覺和…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.63,0:00:33.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來  佳奈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.10,0:00:35.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.28,0:00:37.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  因為熟悉不少了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.46,0:00:43.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？說起來小夢  今天你不是休息日嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.73,0:00:45.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,起得好早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.58,0:00:48.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,稍稍有點事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.10,0:00:51.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.78,0:00:57.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,曲奇看上去好好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.76,0:00:59.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.71,0:01:02.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已經這時間了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.09,0:01:05.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好  我得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.08,0:01:07.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,佳奈  這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.36,0:01:12.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請問  這個要怎麼辦啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.83,0:01:14.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把這個給優希～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.14,0:01:17.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  再見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.26,0:01:24.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  要去哪兒…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.67,0:01:32.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,佳奈  還有一事相求
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.08,0:01:34.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對優希…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.79,0:01:37.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.06,0:01:44.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幫我告訴優希  就算只有她一個人也要努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.97,0:01:54.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶  留下了曲奇的香味
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.59,0:01:58.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小夢像風一般的離去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.67,0:03:37.13,biaoti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(580,405)\fad(500,0)}第一次的、心情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.18,0:03:43.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,佳奈  我去扔垃圾了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.22,0:03:48.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說代理  小夢她剛剛乘著非常豪華的車…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.29,0:03:49.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  已經走了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.57,0:03:51.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,走了是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.29,0:03:54.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就跟你看到的一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.46,0:03:58.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.08,0:04:02.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就跟你說了別東張西望的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.05,0:04:04.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.41,0:04:12.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,清晨就有一大群的少女  而且還是稀有的遠足版的～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.13,0:04:18.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  打擾你們一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.63,0:04:19.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.54,0:04:25.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才小夢上了一輛我從沒見過的閃閃發光的大車子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.35,0:04:28.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咻～咻～地就開走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.81,0:04:31.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來就是今天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.72,0:04:34.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,忘得一乾二淨了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.98,0:04:37.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請問  今天有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.46,0:04:40.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小夢回家去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.80,0:04:41.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,回家了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.91,0:04:45.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對了  佳奈還沒聽說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.13,0:04:47.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.22,0:04:51.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法啊  小夢家是歷史超悠久的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.28,0:04:54.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小夢又是家裡的大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:58.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,家裡人好像無論如何都要她回家去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.20,0:05:00.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,歷史超悠久
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.72,0:05:03.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小夢是大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.17,0:05:06.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,坐上車走了  也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.74,0:05:11.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被帶回家了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.98,0:05:14.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小夢已經走了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.99,0:05:15.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,優希
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.94,0:05:17.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃  那個  這個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.13,0:05:18.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.78,0:05:29.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看來傷得很深啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.72,0:05:30.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.00,0:05:39.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你問怎麼辦…這也是優希成長的一次試煉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.22,0:05:40.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.52,0:05:45.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是她很難受吧  變成一個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.88,0:05:52.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧佳奈  別忍了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.94,0:05:55.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快撲到我胸前來吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.47,0:06:01.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你這人真是  每次都這麼一個模式
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.43,0:06:04.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這叫做相同感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.13,0:06:09.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  味道不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.83,0:06:11.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早飯做好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.93,0:06:13.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.13,0:06:14.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.19,0:06:18.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我去叫小夢和優希
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.02,0:06:21.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小夢不在啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.60,0:06:24.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對…對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.22,0:06:31.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  優希  早飯準備好了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.57,0:06:41.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,優希在哭！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.54,0:06:43.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.69,0:06:46.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然雛田說這是成長的試煉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.92,0:06:49.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是但是  喜歡的人突然不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.54,0:06:51.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還是很痛苦的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.33,0:06:54.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然優希沒有了小夢就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.66,0:07:01.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幫我告訴優希  就算只有她一個人也要努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.13,0:07:06.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那該不會就是小夢給優希的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.52,0:07:09.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,離別贈言嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.43,0:07:12.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你一個人在玩什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.80,0:07:16.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,代…代理  什麼時候來的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.97,0:07:17.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.75,0:07:20.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  你這麼磨磨蹭蹭的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.39,0:07:22.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我都等不及開飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.08,0:07:27.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這曲奇是小夢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.31,0:07:29.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事啊  一點都不甜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.27,0:07:30.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.19,0:07:36.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鹹的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.46,0:07:40.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,曲奇上這一粒一粒的不是砂糖  而是鹽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.05,0:07:43.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這該不會是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.37,0:07:46.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎～呀～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.49,0:07:50.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太過分了  夢夫先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.60,0:07:53.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鹽曲奇的花語是永久的別離
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.09,0:07:55.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你要拋棄我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.56,0:07:56.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.32,0:08:01.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,結束這甜膩膩的生活吧  Baby
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.93,0:08:02.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.41,0:08:06.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要拋棄我  夢夫先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.34,0:08:08.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,放開我  快放手你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.71,0:08:09.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經膩了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.88,0:08:16.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道小夢不是被家裡的人硬帶回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.64,0:08:18.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而是兩個人決裂了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.70,0:08:26.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那個  小夢說這是給優希的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.79,0:08:32.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過好像把砂糖跟鹽弄混了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.28,0:08:35.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.51,0:08:46.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鹽曲奇的花語是永久的別離
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.00,0:08:47.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:49.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦啊代理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:52.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也只能放著不管了囉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.10,0:08:54.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.77,0:09:09.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事都沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.37,0:09:22.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這是為什麼  小夢和優希明明那麼要好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.27,0:09:30.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不對不對不對  不是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.85,0:09:35.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你一個人也要振作這種話我實在說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.69,0:09:37.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,佳奈  你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.79,0:09:38.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.42,0:09:43.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,少了一個人總覺得不對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.82,0:09:47.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要再來一碗味噌湯！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:49.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.34,0:09:51.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快拿抹布擦擦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.33,0:09:53.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己來就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.18,0:09:57.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來這種事經常是小夢做的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.46,0:09:58.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有蚊子！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.71,0:10:02.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.75,0:10:04.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝…謝謝你  佳奈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.86,0:10:05.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她在幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.99,0:10:06.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.22,0:10:08.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看看電視吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.36,0:10:09.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.19,0:10:16.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下一則新聞是被稱為鴛鴦的那對夫婦的離婚問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.37,0:10:17.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看來結果已經出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.39,0:10:20.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幹嘛關了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.37,0:10:25.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這個  我有個很想看的節目
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.44,0:10:27.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行啊  你換台吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.49,0:10:28.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.26,0:10:34.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  遙控器好像壞了誒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.69,0:10:37.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我直接去按電視上的開關吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.56,0:10:40.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小遙！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.51,0:10:44.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.25,0:10:47.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,佳奈？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.45,0:10:50.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這樣就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.26,0:10:54.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到佳奈會允許  人家好高興
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.54,0:10:58.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.45,0:11:06.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小夢的楓糖漿還放在這！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.08,0:11:09.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小遙  咱們來做點更開心的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.99,0:11:11.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來跳舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.45,0:11:18.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我吃好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.68,0:11:22.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  剩了這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:31.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,優希好像很難過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.68,0:11:35.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.64,0:11:37.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這也是沒辦法～啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.55,0:11:41.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是在湯汁留下印跡之前把衣服脫了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.97,0:11:44.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我來幫你～哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.05,0:11:47.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  你在摸哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.91,0:11:50.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看來是擦不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.95,0:11:53.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的味噌湯放了炸豆腐皮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.22,0:11:57.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,佳奈日記佳奈日記！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.99,0:12:00.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,佳奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.81,0:12:02.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,日～記～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.33,0:12:03.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,佳奈日記…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.24,0:12:22.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能露出寂寞的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.39,0:12:24.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在最覺得寂寞的是優希
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.89,0:12:27.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經不是一個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.93,0:12:49.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,文太  飯好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.79,0:13:12.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還是說  我也會再次迎來變成孤身一人的時刻嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.26,0:13:14.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.84,0:13:22.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,佳奈  水燒開了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.92,0:13:25.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.17,0:13:29.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,滿是點點的圖形真傷眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.48,0:13:34.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都這時候啦  中午吃什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.95,0:13:38.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天小遙和雛田都去學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.51,0:13:41.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想就用剩飯做炒飯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.74,0:13:46.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那在你做好之前我接著做賬去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.50,0:13:49.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請問  優希的午飯怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.94,0:13:50.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總之要不要叫上她…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.00,0:13:54.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只能別去管她了唄  這也算是她自作自受
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.37,0:13:58.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.96,0:14:19.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都已經習慣有人離開了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.42,0:14:29.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要是習慣了  是不是就不會感到寂寞了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.72,0:14:55.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別走  別走啊良和先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.27,0:14:59.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要這麼突然分手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.32,0:15:02.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我再也受不了了  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.27,0:15:10.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,與其忍受這寂寞  倒不如…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.38,0:15:12.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,死了算了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.39,0:15:16.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能這樣！不用覺得這麼寂寞啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.93,0:15:20.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  都是我不好！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.61,0:15:22.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你幹嘛呢佳奈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.30,0:15:26.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,電視好像有點不對勁…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.43,0:15:32.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,優希？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:37.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去哪裡  優希
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.06,0:15:40.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.98,0:15:45.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,與其這樣忍受  倒不如…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.16,0:15:47.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,死了算了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.31,0:15:50.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能去啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.06,0:15:52.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不去不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.07,0:15:57.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能讓你去！再怎麼寂寞也不能去死啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.43,0:16:01.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小夢也說了叫你一個人也要加油…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.47,0:16:07.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在這麼下去我會死的  痛死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.96,0:16:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,痛死？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.21,0:16:15.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我跟小夢都跟你說了多少次了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.21,0:16:16.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,叫你趕快去看牙醫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.45,0:16:31.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要——！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.93,0:16:33.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到明天早上都不能吃東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.47,0:16:38.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊  小夢原來只是回家打掃去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.04,0:16:39.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.15,0:16:43.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,本來是想跟優希一起回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.41,0:16:49.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒回去不是挺好的嗎  因為蛀牙腫得那麼厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.91,0:16:51.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要再一個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.13,0:16:57.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.33,0:16:59.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.71,0:17:02.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對了  等會大家來玩這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.70,0:17:04.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是煙花！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.89,0:17:06.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是白天拿的贈品
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.20,0:17:10.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你白天不是去預備校了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.90,0:17:13.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是  算是為去預備校的預備吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.76,0:17:15.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,當做熱身就稍微…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.32,0:17:17.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今年也沒戲了～吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.82,0:17:20.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這不還有半年呢嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.19,0:17:31.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雛田你真喜歡玩那個～啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.53,0:17:34.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個很酷嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.70,0:17:36.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行家果然還是要玩這個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.27,0:17:38.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,蛇煙花～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.42,0:17:47.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,流星啊流星～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.30,0:17:51.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,佳奈不玩煙花嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.36,0:17:53.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我有點怕那種很厲害的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.07,0:17:56.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是很喜歡看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.71,0:18:03.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就玩這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.67,0:18:05.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,線香煙花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.30,0:18:11.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.73,0:18:12.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.77,0:19:14.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天看不見太陽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.93,0:19:21.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是佳奈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.95,0:19:25.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,美華
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.12,0:19:28.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.22,0:19:29.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,偷懶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.04,0:19:33.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有偷懶啦  只是稍微休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.88,0:19:36.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺有點累了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.51,0:19:39.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是精神滿滿的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.87,0:19:42.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不勞動者不得食！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.82,0:19:47.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,美華  要不要稍微休息一下？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.93,0:19:54.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃  選哪個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.24,0:20:02.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,美華  玉米湯和年糕小豆湯你喜歡哪個？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.25,0:20:08.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我肚子也餓了  一起分著吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.14,0:20:13.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,佳奈一定要這樣的話就沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.61,0:20:18.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我會親自替你喝的  感謝我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.91,0:20:22.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那玉米湯和年糕小豆湯…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.27,0:20:27.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都行  挑三揀四就算不上是助人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.36,0:20:35.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也挺想試試這個的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.63,0:20:39.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.54,0:20:42.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,佳奈先喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.49,0:20:44.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了  美華先喝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.98,0:20:47.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是佳奈買的  你先喝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.54,0:20:48.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.97,0:21:06.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真沒辦法  我請客
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.44,0:21:08.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,美華
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.48,0:21:15.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜  中大獎啦  中大獎啦  贈送一罐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.44,0:21:24.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟佳奈在一起就有很多開心事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.42,0:21:27.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.43,0:21:40.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也會是個好天氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.10,0:21:41.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.68,0:21:45.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶  佳奈是獨自一人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.63,0:21:48.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  也是跟大家在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.89,0:21:54.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不知道這到底該覺得寂寞還是高興
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.93,0:21:59.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  總之今天我也很好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.89,0:23:32.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}　　　　　　　　　　　　　   u{\r}\N下一話  「第一次的、看護」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.82,0:23:35.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說到照顧病人  還是不能少了桃子罐頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.04,0:23:35.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,u啦  u  u
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.46,0:23:37.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好想吃  好想一口咬住
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.17,0:23:37.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.82,0:23:39.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,水嫩嫩的少女們～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.73,0:23:39.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小遙？
